<h1>Pages#analysis</h1>
<div class="analysis">
  <div class="analysis-left">
    <div class="analysis-header">
      <h4>If you get this card today, you should look into getting another card before:</h4>
      <p><%= (Date.today + 364).strftime("%d %B %Y") %></p>
      <a href='url' class="btn btn-primary hvr-icon-buzz"><i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-days hvr-icon"></i>Add to Google Calender</a>
    </div>
    <h5>Factors</h5>
    <div class="factors">
      <% if @card_compare.annual_fee_init < @card_compare.annual_fee_after %>
        <div class="factors-container">
          <h5>Annual fees</h5>
          <p class="hvr-pulse-grow">More info<i class="fa-solid fa-angle-down"></i></p>
          <p>This cardâ€™s annual fee is $<%= @card_compare.annual_fee_init.to_i %> in the first year, but will increase to $<%= @card_compare.annual_fee_after.to_i %> in the subsequent years.</p>
          <p>If you cancel before <%= (Date.today + 364).strftime("%d %B %Y") %>, you will avoid the fee increase.</p>
        </div>
      <% end %>
      <% if @card_compare.bonus_point_reward > 0 && (@spending.to_i/30 * @card_compare.bonus_point_time) > @card_compare.bonus_point_spend %>
        <div class="factors-container">
          <h5>Reward Bonus</h5>
          <p class="hvr-pulse-grow">More Info<i class="fa-solid fa-angle-down"></i></p>
          <p>You can earn up to <%=  number_with_delimiter(@card_compare.bonus_point_reward.to_i) %> <%=  @card_compare.reward_category %>points, provided you spend at least $<%=  number_with_delimiter(@card_compare.bonus_point_spend.to_i) %> within <%= number_with_delimiter(@card_compare.bonus_point_time.to_i) %> days.</p>
          <p>Based on your stated spending of $<%=  number_with_delimiter(@spending) %> per month, you will achieve this by <%= @card_compare.bonus_point_spend.fdiv(@spending.to_i/30).to_i %> days.</p>
        </div>
      <% end %>
      <% if @card_compare.cashback_reward > 0 && (@spending.to_i/30 * @card_compare.cashback_time) > @card_compare.cashback_spend%>
        <div class="factors-container">
          <h5>Cashback</h5>
          <p class="hvr-pulse-grow">More info<i class="fa-solid fa-angle-down"></i></p>
          <p>You can earn up to $<%=  number_with_delimiter(@card_compare.cashback_reward.to_i) %> in cashback, provided you spend at least $<%=  number_with_delimiter(@card_compare.cashback_spend.to_i) %> within <%= number_with_delimiter(@card_compare.cashback_time.to_i) %> days.</p>
          <p>Based on your stated spending of $<%=  number_with_delimiter(@spending) %> per month, you will achieve this by <%= @card_compare.cashback_spend.fdiv(@spending.to_i/30).to_i %> days.</p>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
